  - category: 1
    title: Water Rationing
    description: Water supplies are running critically low. You can ration equally
      (everyone suffers a little) or prioritize the children (adults go thirsty).
      What do you decide?
    targetCharacter: 
  - category: 1
    title: Stranger at the Door
    description: Someone is banging on the bunker door begging for help. They claim
